Dialogue: 3,0:00:27.32,0:00:31.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bloody hell Soft drink in hand no alcohol, no cigarettes
Dialogue: 4,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这感觉就像我在一个偏僻的地方做冥想
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It feels like I'm doing dynamic meditation in a hermitage
Dialogue: 4,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}保重，你看起来很帅
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Stay blessed You're looking handsome
Dialogue: 4,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁会只用可乐开派对？
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who throws a party with just cola?
Dialogue: 4,0:00:49.16,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更好的是，还有街上的冰棍
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.16,0:00:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Better than this, would have been ice-pops from the street
Dialogue: 4,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度消费者普拉纳夫非常容易受骗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pranav Bhai, the Indian consumer is very gullible
Dialogue: 4,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是吗?-他会选可乐而不是冰棒
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Is it? - Instead of ice-pops, he will choose cola
Dialogue: 4,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有这些外国公司都在等着把可乐带到印度
Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All these foreign companies are waiting to bring colas to India
Dialogue: 4,0:01:05.24,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:05.24,0:01:06.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Really?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你总是谈生意
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You always talk business
Dialogue: 4,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把生意牵扯进来
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and drag business into everything
Dialogue: 4,0:01:15.24,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等等，你打算投资一家可乐公司吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:15.24,0:01:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hold on Are you planning to invest in a Cola company?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在忘了商业和投资吧
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.72,0:01:20.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Forget business and investment now
Dialogue: 4,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好好享受派对，干杯-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Enjoy the party Drink up - Okay
Dialogue: 4,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我必须要说
Dialogue: 3,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But can I say something?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:26.32,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你根本不会开派对
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.32,0:01:28.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You don't know how to throw a party
Dialogue: 4,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我不知道
Dialogue: 3,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Fine, I don't'
Dialogue: 4,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你要和 Ketan 一起去伦敦，对吗?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You're going to London with Ketan, right? - Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那里你可以尽情狂欢，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There you can party how you want Right?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你喜欢喝什么啤酒？
Dialogue: 3,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's that beer you like?
Dialogue: 4,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请不要提醒我
Dialogue: 3,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please don't remind me
Dialogue: 4,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 百威-对，就是那个
Dialogue: 3,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Budweiser - Yes, that one
Dialogue: 4,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟我想的一样
Dialogue: 3,0:01:41.52,0:01:44.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just what I thought
Dialogue: 4,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}罢工期间我将去伦敦
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll go to London during the strike
Dialogue: 4,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我马上就去
Dialogue: 3,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll make a quick trip
Dialogue: 4,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我只是想知道
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I just got to know
Dialogue: 4,0:01:52.52,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SEBI 和经纪人即将达成和解
Dialogue: 3,0:01:52.52,0:01:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that SEBI and the brokers are close to a settlement
Dialogue: 4,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交易所很快就会开放
Dialogue: 3,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the market is going to open again
Dialogue: 4,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好，我们的 SBI 问题也解决了
Dialogue: 3,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Good Our SBI problem is solved too
Dialogue: 4,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在普拉纳夫大哥，只有一个目标
Dialogue: 3,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now Pranav Bhai, there's only one target
Dialogue: 4,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像公牛一样进入市场，用推土机碾压每个人
Dialogue: 3,0:02:10.88,0:02:13.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To enter the market like a bull and run a bulldozer over everyone
Dialogue: 4,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}清理所有人
Dialogue: 3,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Clean up everyone
Dialogue: 4,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个关于哈沙德和 SBI 的事情
Dialogue: 3,0:02:23.00,0:02:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This talk about Harshad and SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 确认了吗?-百分之百
Dialogue: 3,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Manu] 'Is it confirmed?' - One hundred percent
Dialogue: 4,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔这次会完蛋的
Dialogue: 3,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mehta will be finished this time
Dialogue: 4,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他有大麻烦了
Dialogue: 3,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's in deep shit
Dialogue: 4,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过去几天以来，雷克萨斯一直停在 SBI
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Since the past few days, the Lexus is always at SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们说他经常跑来跑去
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They say that he's been running to and fro so often
Dialogue: 4,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他可能会晕倒
Dialogue: 3,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he might get dizzy and collapse
Dialogue: 4,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他已经归还了一大笔钱，但还剩下一些
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has returned a big chunk, but there is some left
Dialogue: 4,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场关闭了，他也没有在外面做过任何交易
Dialogue: 3,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market is closed and he hasn't made any transactions outside
Dialogue: 4,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你们想做什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, what do you guys want to do?
Dialogue: 4,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人知道他是从哪里得到这笔钱来偿还 SBI 的债务
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody knows where is he getting the money to repay SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他还没有清算任何股票
Dialogue: 3,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He hasn't liquidated any of his stocks
Dialogue: 4,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一旦 SBI 的新闻正式公开
Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once the SBI news officially becomes public
Dialogue: 4,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们就有机会压低哈沙德的股价
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we will have a chance to push down Harshad's stocks
Dialogue: 4,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们会失去对他的信任
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People will lose trust in him
Dialogue: 4,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我认为这是最好的机会
Dialogue: 3,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think this is the best opportunity
Dialogue: 4,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}机会个屁
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Opportunity, my foot
Dialogue: 4,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说话像个傻瓜！
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Spoken like a fool!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们都没有哈沙德的头脑
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}None of you have Harshad's brains
Dialogue: 4,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在新闻发布之前
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Before the news breaks out
Dialogue: 4,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会平仓赚钱
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he'll square off his position and make profits
Dialogue: 4,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在正在罢工
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is a strike
Dialogue: 4,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果市场不开盘，他将如何平仓？
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How will he square off his position if the market doesn't open?
Dialogue: 4,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去他妈的，你们能不能清醒一下
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}F****rs, at least keep yourselves updated
Dialogue: 4,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难道你不知道
Dialogue: 3,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't you know
Dialogue: 4,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经纪人和证券交易所已经达成和解
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the brokers and SEBI have reached a settlement
Dialogue: 4,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场明天开盘
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market will open tomorrow
Dialogue: 4,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和解可以拖延，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The settlement can be dragged on, can't it?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是马努大哥的市场
Dialogue: 3,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's Manu Bhai's market
Dialogue: 4,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你只需要给出一个信号
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You just have to give a signal
Dialogue: 4,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还需要罢工多少天？
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}For how many days will it need to remain closed?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直到消息传出去
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until the news comes out
Dialogue: 4,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场只有在全面恐慌时才能开盘
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market should only open once there is panic all around
Dialogue: 4,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样他在市场上就完蛋了
Dialogue: 3,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He'll be finished in the market
Dialogue: 4,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且他也不能归还SBI剩下的债务
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.32,0:04:28.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and also won't be able to return the money he has taken to repay SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在股票市场上给他一刀
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[AK] 'You kill him in the share market'
Dialogue: 4,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们将在货币市场上再给他一刀
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We will stab him in the money market
Dialogue: 4,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我来处理孟买的事
Dialogue: 3,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll handle Bombay
Dialogue: 4,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是其他的证券交易所呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But what about the other stock exchanges?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}加尔各答交给我吧
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Leave Calcutta to me
Dialogue: 4,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何，焦点都在孟买
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And anyway, everyone will follow BSE
Dialogue: 4,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是这个 SBI 的消息一定要尽快出来
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.36,0:05:02.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But this SBI news should come out soon
Dialogue: 4,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不能让罢工持续太久
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can't hold the strike for too long
Dialogue: 4,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我是来自SBI（印度国家银行）的沙拉德·贝拉里
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I'm Sharad Bellary from SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，带我去见任何人 我时间不多了，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, take me to anyone I don't have much time, Sir
Dialogue: 4,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI 有个大问题，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There is a huge problem at SBI, sir
Dialogue: 4,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请把他带到苏切塔女士的办公室
Dialogue: 3,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please take him to Sucheta ma'am
Dialogue: 4,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你甚至无法想象这个骗局有多大
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.96,0:06:27.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can't even begin to imagine how big the fraud is
Dialogue: 4,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欺诈？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Fraud?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI 的账目上少了50亿卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Five hundred crores are missing from the books of SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道谁是这个骗局的幕后黑手吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know who is behind this fraud?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 3,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}H-Harshad Mehta
Dialogue: 4,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我去给你倒杯茶-我不想喝茶夫人
Dialogue: 3,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I'll get you a cup of tea - I don't want tea, ma'am
Dialogue: 4,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 不，请等一下-夫人，我不想喝茶
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- No, please Just a minute - Ma'am, I don't want tea
Dialogue: 4,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我马上回来，求你了！
Dialogue: 3,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll be right back Please!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好-你好，我是苏切塔
Dialogue: 3,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello - Hello Yeah, Sucheta here
Dialogue: 4,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我们得赶紧叙叙旧
Dialogue: 3,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen, we need to catch up very urgently
Dialogue: 4,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们终于掌握了一些真正的证据
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have finally got some real evidence
Dialogue: 4,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}消息来源就在我面前
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The source is right in front of me
Dialogue: 4,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他说哈尔沙德可能和 SBI 有麻烦了
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and he says Harshad might be in some serious trouble with SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 和 SBI?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- With SBI? - Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他就在这里 我是说，他在我办公室里
Dialogue: 3,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's right here I mean, he is in the cabin
Dialogue: 4,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“我只是需要你给我解释一些技术细节，我们能见个面吗? ”
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'I just need you to explain a few technicalities to me Can we meet?'
Dialogue: 4,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然可以
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah, sure
Dialogue: 4,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，谢谢，再见
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.80,0:07:25.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, thank you Thank you I'll see you, bye
Dialogue: 4,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}坐在这里的那位先生去了哪里？
Dialogue: 3,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where is the gentleman who was sitting here?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给他带了茶，我不知道他去哪了
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I brought tea for him I don't know where he's gone
Dialogue: 4,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，不！
Dialogue: 3,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}出租车！
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Taxi!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喂，是的，请帮我接德巴希？
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello Yes Can you connect me to Debashis, please?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:13.44,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定这个沙拉德·贝拉里在 SBI 总部工作吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.44,0:08:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you sure this Sharat Bellary works at SBI head office?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会不会提供了假消息给你？
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and he hasn't fed you some fake news?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}沙拉德·贝拉里
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sharad "D" Sharad Bellary
Dialogue: 4,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道，但是，听起来很随便
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know but It sounds very convenient to me
Dialogue: 4,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上我认为是照本宣科，听着
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Scripted, in fact Look
Dialogue: 4,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个人不是来自财政部或账户管理部
Dialogue: 3,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not from Treasury or Accounts
Dialogue: 4,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而是一个公关部门的人，来到了印度时报大楼
Dialogue: 3,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But a person from a PR department lands up in TOI building
Dialogue: 4,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}并且只把消息告诉了你一个人
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and gives this story to no one but you
Dialogue: 4,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and then disappears without a word
Dialogue: 4,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Agantuk
Dialogue: 3,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Agantuk
Dialogue: 4,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}意思是“陌生人”
Dialogue: 3,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It means "The Stranger"
Dialogue: 4,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这可能是萨蒂亚吉特 · 雷的最后一部电影
Dialogue: 3,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It might be Satyajit Ray's last film
Dialogue: 4,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道他的情况，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know his condition, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我正在写一篇关于他的文章
Dialogue: 3,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I was writing an article on it for a change
Dialogue: 4,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 被 SBI 的陌生人困住了! 真奇怪！
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and got trapped by SBI's Agantuk! How strange!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我同意这不是巧合
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Agreed This isn't a coincidence
Dialogue: 4,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他被安排到我这里来了，但是不管是谁送他来的
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's been sent to me But whoever has sent him
Dialogue: 4,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个人一定知道只有我能跟进哈沙德的故事
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}knows, that only I can follow up on Harshad's story
Dialogue: 4,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个故事是可以栽赃的，苏切塔
Dialogue: 3,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this story could be planted, Sucheta
Dialogue: 4,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为这个“陌生人”消失的方式
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because the way this 'Sharad', disappeared
Dialogue: 4,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不认为他有任何证据
Dialogue: 3,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't think he had any evidence
Dialogue: 4,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样，你去 SBI 交叉核对？
Dialogue: 3,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do one thing, go to SBI and cross-check?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}交叉核对? 那你呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Cross-check? And what about you?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我现在不能去，我得和我的线人谈谈
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't go right now I have to talk to my source
Dialogue: 4,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要他解释一些贝拉里告诉我的事情
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need him to explain a few things that Bellary was telling me
Dialogue: 4,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 3,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay
Dialogue: 4,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们先去见见线人，然后再去 SBI
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's meet Karamchand first, and then go to SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你得一个人去，我们没时间了
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Debashis, you'll have to go alone We are don't have time
Dialogue: 4,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 快去SBI-好的我去
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.16,0:09:36.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Please go to SBI - Okay, I'll go
Dialogue: 4,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我先喝杯茶
Dialogue: 3,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let me have tea first
Dialogue: 4,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去 SBI 喝茶，他们的茶真的很好喝
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have tea at SBI Their tea is really good
Dialogue: 4,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你现在走，还可能会遇到哈萨德
Dialogue: 3,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And if you go now, you might run into Harshad
Dialogue: 4,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟他一起喝茶吧
Dialogue: 3,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have a couple of sips with him too Please
Dialogue: 4,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}求你了
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please
Dialogue: 4,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 拜托，德巴希斯，快去吧-我这就去
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Please, Debashis, go - I'm going I'm going!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我能喝这个吗?-请便
