Dialogue: 3,0:10:49.84,0:10:50.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Debashis
Dialogue: 4,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是他表弟，从加尔各答来的
