Dialogue: 4,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我住在那里，今晚坐火车回去，所以我想见见沙拉德大哥
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I live there I'm taking a train back tonight so I thought Sharad Bhai
Dialogue: 4,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女士 有点急事
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Ma'am It's a bit urgent, please
Dialogue: 4,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-他在哪个部门?-公关部
Dialogue: 3,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Which department did you say? - PR
Dialogue: 4,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等一下
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Receptionist] 'One second'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:04.52,0:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你好，沙拉德·贝拉里的表弟来看他了”
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.52,0:11:08.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Hello Sharad Bellary's cousin is here to see him'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}德巴希斯
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Debashis'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生，他不在办公室
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay Sir, he's not in office
Dialogue: 4,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他出去了
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He left a while ago
Dialogue: 4,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他还没回来吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- He hasn't come back yet?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，他告诉我他要出去，但是
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, he had told me that he's going out but
Dialogue: 4,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他现在应该已经回来了
Dialogue: 3,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he should have been back by now
Dialogue: 4,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No problem
Dialogue: 4,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去他的办公室里等
Dialogue: 3,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll do one thing, I'll wait in his cabin
Dialogue: 4,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“先生，他没有办公室”
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Receptionist] 'Sir, he doesn't have a cabin'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好吧!-那……
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay! - 'So'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我去他的座位等
Dialogue: 3,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So I'll wait at his desk
Dialogue: 4,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你哪儿也不能去，你得在这儿等着
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Sir, you can't go anywhere, You'll have to wait here'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay - 'Yes'
Dialogue: 4,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那笔钱是怎么进入他的帐户的？
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How did that money go into his account?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度国家银行会以旁遮普国家银行的名义签发支票，对吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI would have issued the cheques in PNB's name, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德只是个经纪人
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is just a broker
Dialogue: 4,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此印度国家银行必须直接以哈尔沙德的名义签发支票
Dialogue: 3,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because SBI must have issued the cheques directly in Harshad's name
Dialogue: 4,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是违法的吗? 这不是错的吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Isn't that illegal? Is it not wrong?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧！
Dialogue: 3,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是公认的市场行为
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's an accepted market practice
Dialogue: 4,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“你看，当系统效率低下时  ”
Dialogue: 3,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'You see, when the system is inefficient'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} 人们就从内部找到漏洞把它扭曲一点点
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}people from within, tweak it They twist and bend it a little
Dialogue: 4,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样业务才能顺利进行
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'So that business can carry on smoothly'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}做生意的便利性
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Ease of doing business'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种交易是建立在信任的基础上的
Dialogue: 3,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Such transactions work on trust
Dialogue: 4,0:12:13.56,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而在商业领域，信任比所有的法律规定都重要
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.56,0:12:17.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And in business, trust is bigger than all legalities
Dialogue: 4,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}问题出现在
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The problem arises when
Dialogue: 4,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像哈尔沙德 · 梅塔这样的人滥用这个平行系统并将其变成犯罪
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}people like Harshad Mehta misuse this parallel system and turn it into a crime
Dialogue: 4,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他破坏了体制的信任
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'You know, they They break the trust of the system'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}打破了平衡
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'They They ruin the equilibrium'
Dialogue: 4,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管怎样，这都是错误的，不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Either way, this is wrong, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行只能与其他银行进行交易
Dialogue: 3,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Banks can only transact with other banks
Dialogue: 4,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们怎么能以经纪人的名义直接签发支票呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can they issue cheques directly in the name of a broker?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为，有时候，为了节省时间，银行会把钱转到经纪人的账户上
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because, sometimes, to save time, banks transfer money into the broker's account
Dialogue: 4,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后就是经纪人的事情了，要给银行带来最好的交易
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and then it's the broker's headache, how he gets them the best deals
Dialogue: 4,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以
Dialogue: 3,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So
Dialogue: 4,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以只要钱在经纪人的账户里
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, as long as the money is in the broker's account
Dialogue: 4,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他可以把钱投资到任何他想投资的地方？
Dialogue: 3,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he can invest it wherever he wants?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错，每个人都这么做
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Correct, everyone does this
Dialogue: 4,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个人？
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Everyone?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别那样看着我，我也一样
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't look at me like that Even I do it
Dialogue: 4,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我要确保自己不会辜负体系的信任
Dialogue: 3,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I make sure I don't break the trust of the system
Dialogue: 4,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“我不会破坏它的平衡”
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'I don't disturb its balance'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，我想
Dialogue: 3,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, I think
Dialogue: 4,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你走错方向了，问题不在于
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}you're taking the wrong direction here The problem here is not
Dialogue: 4,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI 把钱转到了哈尔沙德的账户
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.24,0:13:25.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that SBI transferred money into Harshad's account Okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，他们之间过去一定有很多这样的交易
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, there must have been many such transactions between them in the past
Dialogue: 4,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}至少五百到一千亿卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At least five to ten thousand crores
Dialogue: 4,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是为什么，这一次，他们在他的帐户存入了50亿卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why, this time also, they deposited 500 crores in his account
Dialogue: 4,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}假设他拿到了证券，他会把钱还回来
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}assuming he has the securities and he will return the money
Dialogue: 4,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我不认为他有这些证券
Dialogue: 3,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I don't think he has those securities
Dialogue: 4,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“而且我认为旁遮普国家银行对此一无所知”
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'And I don't think PNB even knows anything about this'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这太疯狂了
Dialogue: 3,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That is crazy
Dialogue: 4,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:13:49.00,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想 SBI 已经听到风声了，所以他们要求他把钱还回去
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.00,0:13:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think SBI has caught wind of it That's why they're asking him to return the money
Dialogue: 4,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“你听说过假冒的BR吧? ”
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'You had heard about fake BRs?'
Dialogue: 4,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而这是第一次，BR根本不存在
Dialogue: 3,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the first time that, the BRs don't exist at all
Dialogue: 4,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是一个骗局！
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now that is a scam!
