Dialogue: 3,0:14:31.52,0:14:32.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Which department?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是贝拉里先生的表弟
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm Bellary ji's cousin
Dialogue: 4,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}贝拉里? 哪个贝拉里？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bellary? Who Bellary?
