Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sharad Bellary
Dialogue: 4,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}沙拉德 · 贝拉里？
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sharad Bellary?
