Dialogue: 4,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是他的超级粉丝
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm a big fan
Dialogue: 4,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-哈尔沙德·梅塔?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Harshad Mehta? - Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他开进口的雷克萨斯来了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Has he come in his imported Lexus?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know
Dialogue: 4,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，我得走了，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry, I have to leave Thank you
Dialogue: 4,0:15:39.80,0:15:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:15:39.80,0:15:40.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh Thank you
Dialogue: 4,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是哪个部门的？
Dialogue: 3,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Which department?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- HR-好的
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- HR - Okay
Dialogue: 4,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我以前没见过你
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I haven't seen you before
Dialogue: 4,0:15:50.48,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真巧，我也没见过你
Dialogue: 3,0:15:50.48,0:15:54.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What a coincidence I haven't seen you either
Dialogue: 4,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，不，我上个月才入职的
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh no, no I just joined last month
Dialogue: 4,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，好吧，那不奇怪，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, okay No wonder Thanks
Dialogue: 4,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去打几个电话
Dialogue: 3,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll make a few phone calls
Dialogue: 4,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果获取到更多的信息，我会告诉你的
Dialogue: 3,0:16:09.64,0:16:11.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll let you know if I get some more information
Dialogue: 4,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会和我在市场上的熟人谈谈
Dialogue: 3,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I'll talk to my contacts in the market
Dialogue: 4,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}另外我还要和哈沙德谈谈
Dialogue: 3,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Plus, I need to talk to Harshad as well
Dialogue: 4,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要直接跟他谈吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You'll talk to him directly?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是他的故事，我需要知道他的立场
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The story is on him, I need to know his side as well
Dialogue: 4,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一篇调查报道
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this is an investigative piece
Dialogue: 4,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果不知道他是怎么说的，听起来就像是流言蜚语
Dialogue: 3,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without knowing his side of the story, it'll seem like gossip
Dialogue: 4,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想让人觉得我是那种记者，所以
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't want to seem like that kind of a journalist So
Dialogue: 4,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 谢谢-祝你好运
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Thanks - Good luck
Dialogue: 4,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}改变世界
Dialogue: 3,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Change the world
Dialogue: 4,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我一定会努力的
Dialogue: 3,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I will surely try
Dialogue: 4,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好-你好，梅塔先生？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello - Hello, Mr Mehta?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 请讲-我是苏切塔 · 达拉尔
Dialogue: 3,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Speaking - This is Sucheta Dalal
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在方便讲话吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is this a good time to talk?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这取决于这个电话是建设性的还是破坏性的？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Depends Is this call constructive or destructive?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生我只是想确认一下
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta, I just wanted to check
Dialogue: 4,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们刚刚得知你们未能如期交付
Dialogue: 3,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We've just been informed that you've failed to deliver securities
Dialogue: 4,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}价值50亿卢比的证券给印度国家银行
Dialogue: 3,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'worth 500 crores to the State Bank of India'
Dialogue: 4,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在他们要求退款，你对此有什么回应吗
Dialogue: 3,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'And now they're demanding their money back Would you care to comment?'
Dialogue: 4,0:17:22.20,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有
Dialogue: 3,0:17:22.20,0:17:22.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No
Dialogue: 4,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:24.16,0:17:24.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why not?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为这毫无根据，毫无意义
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because it's baseless, it's nonsense
Dialogue: 4,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像你这样的记者不适合煽动这种谣言
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it doesn't suit a journalist like you to fan such rumours
Dialogue: 4,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你确定吗梅塔先生? 因为我有线人
Dialogue: 3,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you sure, Mr Mehta? Because I have sources
Dialogue: 4,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许能证实这一点
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}who might be able to confirm this
Dialogue: 4,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“听着，你想要我的回应，我给你了”
Dialogue: 3,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Look, you wanted my reaction and you got it'
Dialogue: 4,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，你想让我说一些你可以发表的东西
Dialogue: 3,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, you want me to say something that you can print
Dialogue: 4,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI 知道真相，我也知道
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI knows the truth, and so do I
Dialogue: 4,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么说你否认了？
Dialogue: 3,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So you're denying it?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:49.16,0:17:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔女士，在金融世界里没有空间听这种无聊的闲言碎语
Dialogue: 3,0:17:49.16,0:17:53.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta ji, there's no room for such filmy gossip in the financial world
Dialogue: 4,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你的消息来源是谁?-谢谢，梅塔先生
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Anyway, who is your source? - Thank you, Mr Mehta
Dialogue: 4,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，如果这篇文章发表了，就会打开潘多拉的盒子
Dialogue: 3,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, if this gets published it'll open a pandora's box
Dialogue: 4,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么都不会发表
Dialogue: 3,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nothing will get published
Dialogue: 4,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 没有消息-似乎有
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- There is no news - There seems to be
Dialogue: 4,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}她听起来很坚决
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}She sounded determined
Dialogue: 4,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以我才叫你别偷听我的电话
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why I ask you not to eavesdrop on my calls
Dialogue: 4,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果她有证据，她会直接发表的，不会打电话给我
Dialogue: 3,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If she had proof, she would have published it She wouldn't have called me
Dialogue: 4,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们知道我在这个行业里是个大人物
Dialogue: 3,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They know that I'm the real deal in this business
Dialogue: 4,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他们在没有证据的情况下发表任何东西，他们就有麻烦了
Dialogue: 3,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If they publish anything without proof, they'll be in trouble
Dialogue: 4,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你还在等什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让他们知道你不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Show them that you're the real deal
Dialogue: 4,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔？
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}接过来
Dialogue: 3,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Put him through
Dialogue: 4,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}50亿，你在开玩笑吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}500 crores Are you joking?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，可能会更多
Dialogue: 3,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen It can be even more
Dialogue: 4,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，有可能我自己也见过他几次
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, it's possible I've seen him a few times myself
Dialogue: 4,0:19:09.28,0:19:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}三天前，有一大群人只是为了看看他的车
Dialogue: 3,0:19:09.28,0:19:12.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Three days back, there was a crowd just to look at his car
Dialogue: 4,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 哪辆车-雷克萨斯
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Which car is it - Lexus
Dialogue: 4,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，雷克萨斯
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Lexus
Dialogue: 4,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是谁告诉你这50亿的？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But who told you about this 500 crore?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兄弟，每个人都知道，但他们保持沉默
Dialogue: 3,0:19:18.20,0:19:20.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Brother, everyone knows, but they are keeping mum
Dialogue: 4,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为如果事情曝光，有些高级官员会受到惩罚
Dialogue: 3,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because if it becomes public, even the senior officials will get f****d
Dialogue: 4,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你是认真的吗?-嗯
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-Are you serious? -Hmmm
Dialogue: 4,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}西塔拉曼先生，来这边
Dialogue: 3,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sitaraman ji, please come
Dialogue: 4,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 那是谁?-他什么都知道
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Who's that? - He will know everything
Dialogue: 4,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们正在谈论你的部门
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We were just talking about your department
Dialogue: 4,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 是吗? 你们在说什么?-是的
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Is it? What were you talking about? - Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还是老样子，哈尔沙德 · 梅塔的案子
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The same Harshad Mehta case
Dialogue: 4,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 这位先生说金额有50亿-胡说！
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- This gentleman here says, 500 crores have - Nonsense!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}绝对的谣言
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Absolute rubbish
Dialogue: 4,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}除了在餐厅里闲聊，你就没别的事可做了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.40,0:19:46.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't you have anything better to do, than gossip in the canteen?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mehta 先生和 SBI 做了很多生意
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Mehta and SBI do a lot of business
Dialogue: 4,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，有时会计会出错，但现在一切都解决了
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So sometimes the accounting goes wrong, but it's all settled now
Dialogue: 4,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的吗? 50亿他都还清了？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All of it? All 500 crores?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，还有一点未结清，只有六七千万卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, a little is pending Only six or seven crores
Dialogue: 4,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这两天就会结清了
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That will be done day after tomorrow
Dialogue: 4,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们最好别再散布谣言了
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You guys better stop spreading these rumours
Dialogue: 4,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果卡马尼先生知道这件事，他会让你们俩停职
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If Mr Khemani hears about this he will suspend you both
Dialogue: 4,0:20:10.48,0:20:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这是他说的，跟我们没关系
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.48,0:20:15.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, he was saying What do we care? It's not even our department
Dialogue: 4,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right
Dialogue: 4,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你来自哪个部门？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Which department are you from?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公关部
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}PR
Dialogue: 4,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你刚不是说人力资源部？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}HR?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的 我加入才几天
Dialogue: 3,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes It's only been a few days since I joined
Dialogue: 4,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}公关还是人力资源？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}PR or HR?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人力资源
Dialogue: 3,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}HR
Dialogue: 4,0:20:40.44,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 喝点茶吧-不了，我有急事
Dialogue: 3,0:20:40.44,0:20:43.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Have some tea at least - No, I have something urgent to do
Dialogue: 4,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我也该走了，我还有很多工作要做
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, I should leave too I have a lot of work to do
Dialogue: 4,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 谢谢-最近有新员工入职你们部门吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Thank you - Has anyone joined your department recently?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有，怎么了？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, why?
Dialogue: 4,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那边那个人，不是你们部门的吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That man over there Isn't he from your department?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的
Dialogue: 3,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay -[typewriter clicking]
Dialogue: 4,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 两年前-好的明白了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Two years back Okay, got it
Dialogue: 4,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好了，我一会儿再打给你
Dialogue: 3,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay No, listen I'll have to call you back
Dialogue: 4,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎样? 我们还是去会议室谈吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So? Actually, you know what, let's talk in the conference room
Dialogue: 4,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 为什么?-来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But why? - Come Just come
Dialogue: 4,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 怎么了?-只是 人太多了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What happened? - Just too many people
Dialogue: 4,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“不行”
Dialogue: 3,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'No'
Dialogue: 4,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想他在见过你之后就消失了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think he's disappeared after meeting you
Dialogue: 4,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是苏切塔，贝拉里似乎说的是实话
Dialogue: 3,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But Sucheta, Bellary seems to be telling the truth
Dialogue: 4,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德经常去SBI
Dialogue: 3,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad has been regularly visiting SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:21:33.64,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}似乎有什么隐情
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.64,0:21:37.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}meetings are happening Something seems to be brewing
Dialogue: 4,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-拿到任何证据了吗?-没有
Dialogue: 3,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So what do we have now? - Nothing much
Dialogue: 4,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德会签出最后一张支票，数额很小
Dialogue: 3,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is giving the last cheque day after tomorrow It's a small amount
Dialogue: 4,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的债务也会被清偿，到时候就没有报道了
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And his dues will be cleared up There's no news
Dialogue: 4,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果罪犯清理了犯罪现场
Dialogue: 3,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If a criminal cleans up the crime scene
Dialogue: 4,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是否意味着犯罪行为从未发生过？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}does that mean the crime never happened?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他滥用体系漏洞，把这个体系搞得一团糟
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has messed with the system and misused it
Dialogue: 4,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 所以他才要还钱-告诉我
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why he is repaying the money Tell me one thing, Debashis
Dialogue: 4,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些资金来自哪里？
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where are the funds coming from?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每一分钱都属于印度人民
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Every single penny belongs to the people of India
Dialogue: 4,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他怎么能像用他爸的钱一样随便呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can he use it like his father's money?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他想用就用，赚了钱就还上！
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Used it whenever he wanted, earned profit on it and returned it!
Dialogue: 4,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他亏损了怎么办? 如果他还不回去怎么办？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if he had made a loss? What if he couldn't have returned it?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:11.00,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，一旦剩下的钱还清，我们就没有报道了
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.00,0:22:14.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, once the rest of the money is returned, we don't have a story
Dialogue: 4,0:22:14.80,0:22:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就这么简单
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.80,0:22:15.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As simple as that
Dialogue: 4,0:22:16.64,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为 SBI 的人会开口吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.64,0:22:20.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think the people at SBI will speak about this?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要确保今晚这个故事能够公之于众
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is why I'm going to make sure the story comes out tonight
Dialogue: 4,0:22:25.16,0:22:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在他把剩下的钱还回来之前
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.16,0:22:26.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}before he returns the rest of the money
Dialogue: 4,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好！
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello!
Dialogue: 4,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，我们是在做关于哈尔沙德·梅塔的报道吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, are we doing a story on Harshad Mehta?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:38.84,0:22:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你怎么知道的? ”
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.84,0:22:39.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'How did you know?'
Dialogue: 4,0:22:39.84,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他打来了电话，否认了一切
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.84,0:22:41.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He called, he denied everything
Dialogue: 4,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有他的证词吗，他到底否认了什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have his statement, what has he denied exactly?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你有什么证据支持你的说法吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you have anything to support your story?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:47.76,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有消息来源
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.76,0:22:48.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have my sources
Dialogue: 4,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的线人能公开发言吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Will they speak on record?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:51.08,0:22:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能，但我通过多种渠道交叉核对了所有信息
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.08,0:22:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No But I've cross-checked all the facts through multiple channels
Dialogue: 4,0:22:54.32,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，你要知道，这是印度时报
Dialogue: 3,0:22:54.32,0:22:56.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, you need to understand this is the Times of India
Dialogue: 4,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有实际的书面证据，不能发表任何东西
Dialogue: 3,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without actual paper evidence, you can't print anything
Dialogue: 4,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能让你继续
Dialogue: 3,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't give you the go-ahead
Dialogue: 4,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我对我的资料来源有信心，在过去，我们发表过
Dialogue: 3,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have faith in my sources and in the past, people have published
Dialogue: 4,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有任何书面证据的很多文章
Dialogue: 3,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}many articles without any paper evidence
Dialogue: 4,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我希望你能理解，如果消息不是真的
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I hope you understand that he can even sue us
Dialogue: 4,0:23:06.72,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他甚至可以起诉我们
Dialogue: 3,0:23:06.72,0:23:07.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}if the news is not true
Dialogue: 4,0:23:08.68,0:23:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉杰迪普，如果你不让我发表
Dialogue: 3,0:23:08.68,0:23:10.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rajdeep, if you won't let me publish this
Dialogue: 4,0:23:10.60,0:23:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我就去找迪里普了
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.60,0:23:11.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}then I'm going to have to go to Dileep
Dialogue: 4,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，去吧，我相信他也会这么说的
Dialogue: 3,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure, go for it I'm sure he'll say the same thing
Dialogue: 4,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不会公开宣称‘我们是最勇敢的’
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We don't claim publicly that 'we are the most courageous'
Dialogue: 4,0:23:23.76,0:23:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是如果这个国家有一家新闻出版社采取强硬立场
Dialogue: 3,0:23:23.76,0:23:28.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But if there is a news publication in this country that takes a tough stance
Dialogue: 4,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我们就是救世主
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}then we are the one
Dialogue: 4,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不区分强者和弱者
Dialogue: 3,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We don't differentiate between the powerful and the weak
Dialogue: 4,0:23:34.44,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们的报纸最近是不是太亲政府了？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.44,0:23:39.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hasn't your newspaper been too pro-government lately?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，他们一直是亲政府的
Dialogue: 3,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, they were always pro-government
Dialogue: 4,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迪里普，告诉我
Dialogue: 3,0:23:43.20,0:23:44.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Dileep, tell me something
Dialogue: 4,0:23:45.40,0:23:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}英国人还在支付你的薪水吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:23:45.40,0:23:49.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are the British still paying your salary?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们和别人的区别是
Dialogue: 3,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The difference between others and us is
Dialogue: 4,0:23:54.12,0:23:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不再无意义地批评政府
Dialogue: 3,0:23:54.12,0:23:57.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}that we don't keep on criticising the government pointlessly
Dialogue: 4,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不仅仅是为了指出系统中的缺陷
Dialogue: 3,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are not here to just point out the faults in the system
Dialogue: 4,0:24:00.04,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托 迪里普先生
Dialogue: 3,0:24:00.04,0:24:02.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh Come on Mr Dileep
Dialogue: 4,0:24:02.64,0:24:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把这些政治上正确的答案留给我们这些政客吧
Dialogue: 3,0:24:02.64,0:24:06.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Leave these politically correct answers to us politicians
Dialogue: 4,0:24:06.84,0:24:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:06.84,0:24:07.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Am I right?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，帕德冈卡先生
Dialogue: 3,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry, Mr Padgaonkar
Dialogue: 4,0:24:10.08,0:24:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但你一定听说过那句话
Dialogue: 3,0:24:10.08,0:24:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you must have heard the saying
Dialogue: 4,0:24:12.72,0:24:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}《泰晤士报》就像风一样？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.72,0:24:15.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"The Times" flows the way the wind blows Huh?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:16.00,0:24:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}实际上，《时代》是按照《时代》的方式发展的
Dialogue: 3,0:24:16.00,0:24:20.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Actually, "The Time" flows the way "The Times" goes
Dialogue: 4,0:24:22.80,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，您有一个从孟买打来的重要电话
Dialogue: 3,0:24:22.80,0:24:25.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr Padgaonkar, you have an important call from Bombay
Dialogue: 4,0:24:25.96,0:24:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，先生们，我有个电话要接
Dialogue: 3,0:24:25.96,0:24:28.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Excuse me, gentlemen I have a call to take
Dialogue: 4,0:24:30.32,0:24:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好-你好
Dialogue: 3,0:24:30.32,0:24:31.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello - Hello
Dialogue: 4,0:24:31.84,0:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我是苏切塔
Dialogue: 3,0:24:31.84,0:24:33.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, Sucheta here
Dialogue: 4,0:24:33.24,0:24:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，很抱歉打扰你，但这是非常紧急的事情
Dialogue: 3,0:24:33.24,0:24:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, sorry to bother you but this is very urgent
Dialogue: 4,0:24:36.00,0:24:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔 · 达拉尔？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:36.00,0:24:37.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta Dalal?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:37.52,0:24:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生，从孟买打来的
Dialogue: 3,0:24:37.52,0:24:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Yes, sir, from Bombay'
Dialogue: 4,0:24:39.44,0:24:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么知道我在这儿？
Dialogue: 3,0:24:39.44,0:24:40.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How did you know I'm here?
Dialogue: 4,0:24:40.72,0:24:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，说来话长现在，我想跟您讨论一些重要的事情
Dialogue: 3,0:24:40.72,0:24:43.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, it's a long story Right now, I want to discuss something important
Dialogue: 4,0:24:44.00,0:24:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续，我在听
Dialogue: 3,0:24:44.00,0:24:45.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'Go ahead, I'm listening'
Dialogue: 4,0:24:45.52,0:24:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我有个独家新闻
Dialogue: 3,0:24:45.52,0:24:46.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I have a scoop
Dialogue: 4,0:24:47.16,0:24:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德·梅塔诈骗了 SBI 五十亿卢比
Dialogue: 3,0:24:47.16,0:24:49.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta has defrauded SBI of 500 crores
Dialogue: 4,0:24:50.36,0:24:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“没有人对此有丝毫的暗示”
Dialogue: 3,0:24:50.36,0:24:52.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'and no one has the slightest hint about it'
Dialogue: 4,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有一个主要消息来源，来自印度国家银行的公关部门
Dialogue: 3,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have a primary source from the SBI, PR department
Dialogue: 4,0:24:55.92,0:24:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他今天上午来到办公室，把所有的细节都告诉了我
Dialogue: 3,0:24:55.92,0:24:58.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He came into office this morning and gave me all the details
Dialogue: 4,0:24:58.36,0:24:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我真的很想继续这个故事
Dialogue: 3,0:24:58.36,0:24:59.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I really want to go ahead with this story
Dialogue: 4,0:25:00.84,0:25:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那又怎样? 有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 3,0:25:00.84,0:25:02.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'So? What's the problem?'
Dialogue: 4,0:25:02.88,0:25:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，拉杰迪普不同意
Dialogue: 3,0:25:02.88,0:25:04.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, Rajdeep is not agreeing
Dialogue: 4,0:25:04.36,0:25:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他说因为我没有任何书面证据
Dialogue: 3,0:25:04.36,0:25:06.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He says that because I don't have any paper evidence
Dialogue: 4,0:25:06.20,0:25:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能让我继续报道这件事
Dialogue: 3,0:25:06.20,0:25:07.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}he cannot allow me to go forward with the story
Dialogue: 4,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你没有证据？
Dialogue: 3,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have no evidence?
Dialogue: 4,0:25:10.56,0:25:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你的线人……”
Dialogue: 3,0:25:10.56,0:25:11.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'Your source'
Dialogue: 4,0:25:13.60,0:25:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有，但是我已经做了全面的背景调查，我很确定
Dialogue: 3,0:25:13.60,0:25:17.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, sir But I've done a complete background check I'm sure of this
Dialogue: 4,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我明白，苏切塔”
Dialogue: 3,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'I understand, Sucheta'
Dialogue: 4,0:25:20.44,0:25:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但还是试着找到一些证据
Dialogue: 3,0:25:20.44,0:25:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But try and find some evidence of any kind
Dialogue: 4,0:25:23.96,0:25:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有证据，我们不能发表这么大的报道
Dialogue: 3,0:25:23.96,0:25:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Without any evidence, we can't publish a story this big
Dialogue: 4,0:25:27.64,0:25:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你应该明白这一点”
Dialogue: 3,0:25:27.64,0:25:28.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'You should understand that'
Dialogue: 4,0:25:29.48,0:25:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，但是这个故事明天就会过时
Dialogue: 3,0:25:29.48,0:25:31.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, but this story will be dead by tomorrow
Dialogue: 4,0:25:31.52,0:25:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德正在调整资金
Dialogue: 3,0:25:31.52,0:25:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is retuning the funds
Dialogue: 4,0:25:33.36,0:25:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明天，他就会把最后一张支票存进去
Dialogue: 3,0:25:33.36,0:25:35.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and by the day after, he'll have deposited the last cheque as well
Dialogue: 4,0:25:36.16,0:25:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么就没有报道了
Dialogue: 3,0:25:36.16,0:25:37.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, there's no story then
Dialogue: 4,0:25:38.52,0:25:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他把钱拿走了，又把钱还回去了
Dialogue: 3,0:25:38.52,0:25:40.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He took the money, and has returned it back
Dialogue: 4,0:25:42.36,0:25:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不是一笔他可以随时归还的贷款
Dialogue: 3,0:25:42.36,0:25:44.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This isn't a loan that he can return whenever he wants
Dialogue: 4,0:25:45.04,0:25:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他滥用政府的钱来操纵证券交易所的股价
Dialogue: 3,0:25:45.04,0:25:48.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He's misusing money from the government to rig shares in the stock exchange
Dialogue: 4,0:25:48.84,0:25:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你觉得这是他第一次这么做吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:25:48.84,0:25:51.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And do you think this is his first time he's done it?
Dialogue: 4,0:25:51.32,0:25:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}或者他只是和 SBI 一起做了这件事，以后不会再犯了？
Dialogue: 3,0:25:51.32,0:25:53.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Or that he has only done it with SBI and won't repeat it ever!?
Dialogue: 4,0:25:53.96,0:25:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生哈尔沙德·梅塔人脉很广
Dialogue: 3,0:25:53.96,0:25:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, Harshad Mehta is very well connected
Dialogue: 4,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}银行方面拿他没办法，但是我们可以
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}SBI won't do anything but we can
Dialogue: 4,0:25:59.80,0:26:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们记者什么时候开始不追查
Dialogue: 3,0:25:59.80,0:26:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, when did we journalists stop going after criminals
Dialogue: 4,0:26:02.52,0:26:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些没人向当局举报的罪犯了
Dialogue: 3,0:26:02.52,0:26:04.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}just because nobody has reported them to the authorities
Dialogue: 4,0:26:06.08,0:26:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我给你出个主意
Dialogue: 3,0:26:06.08,0:26:07.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll give you a solution
Dialogue: 4,0:26:08.00,0:26:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}打电话给 SBI，直接询问他们是否与哈尔沙德·梅塔
Dialogue: 3,0:26:08.00,0:26:11.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Call up SBI and ask them directly if such a transaction took place
Dialogue: 4,0:26:11.76,0:26:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}进行了这样的交易 
Dialogue: 3,0:26:11.76,0:26:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}between them and Mr Mehta
Dialogue: 4,0:26:13.84,0:26:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[迪里普]“应该由某位高级官员确认”
Dialogue: 3,0:26:13.84,0:26:16.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Dileep] 'Confirmation should be from some high official'
Dialogue: 4,0:26:17.72,0:26:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果他们确认了，我们就继续
Dialogue: 3,0:26:17.72,0:26:19.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'If they confirm it, we go ahead'
Dialogue: 4,0:26:20.96,0:26:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则，我们就不能发表
Dialogue: 3,0:26:20.96,0:26:22.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Otherwise, we cannot do it
Dialogue: 4,0:26:23.64,0:26:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生，知道了，谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:26:23.64,0:26:25.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, sir Got it Thank you
Dialogue: 4,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不同意，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He didn't agree, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:35.84,0:26:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他希望 SBI 的高级管理层予以确认
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.84,0:26:38.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He wants confirmation from SBI's senior management
Dialogue: 4,0:26:39.44,0:26:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么不直接和印度国家银行的主席谈呢？
Dialogue: 3,0:26:39.44,0:26:42.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why don't you talk to the SBI chairman directly?
Dialogue: 4,0:26:44.60,0:26:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}萨切塔，在今天的版面进入印刷之前，你只有一个小时
Dialogue: 3,0:26:44.60,0:26:48.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, you only have one hour before today's edition goes into printing
Dialogue: 4,0:26:48.52,0:26:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}否则你的故事就完了
Dialogue: 3,0:26:48.52,0:26:50.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}otherwise, your story will be dead
Dialogue: 4,0:26:50.12,0:26:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗? 碰碰运气，祝你好运
Dialogue: 3,0:26:50.12,0:26:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Alright? Take a chance Best of luck
Dialogue: 4,0:27:06.44,0:27:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，有你的电话
Dialogue: 3,0:27:06.44,0:27:07.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, there's a call for you
Dialogue: 4,0:27:11.96,0:27:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好
Dialogue: 3,0:27:11.96,0:27:12.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello
Dialogue: 4,0:27:13.52,0:27:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，晚上好，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:27:13.52,0:27:15.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello Good evening, sir
Dialogue: 4,0:27:15.00,0:27:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是印度时报的苏切塔 · 达拉尔
Dialogue: 3,0:27:15.00,0:27:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is Sucheta Dalal from Times of India
Dialogue: 4,0:27:17.88,0:27:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，达拉尔女士，我能为你做些什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:17.88,0:27:19.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, Ms Dalal, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:20.32,0:27:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我直说了，哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是否诈骗了 SBI
Dialogue: 3,0:27:20.32,0:27:23.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, let me be direct Is it true that Harshad Mehta defrauded SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:27:23.76,0:27:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-  50亿卢比?-什么？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:23.76,0:27:25.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- of 500 crores? - What?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:26.00,0:27:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我不这么认为
Dialogue: 3,0:27:26.00,0:27:27.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, I do not think this is true at all
Dialogue: 4,0:27:27.92,0:27:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你从哪里得到的信息？
Dialogue: 3,0:27:27.92,0:27:29.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where do you get your information from?
Dialogue: 4,0:27:29.96,0:27:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我有线人
Dialogue: 3,0:27:29.96,0:27:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I have a source
Dialogue: 4,0:27:31.56,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你被消息来源误导了，达拉尔女士
Dialogue: 3,0:27:31.56,0:27:34.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your source must be misinformed, Ms Dalal
Dialogue: 4,0:27:34.60,0:27:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们之间有非常大量的交易
Dialogue: 3,0:27:34.60,0:27:37.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, we have very heavy transactions
Dialogue: 4,0:27:37.84,0:27:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时会出现延迟收款的情况
Dialogue: 3,0:27:37.84,0:27:42.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and sometimes reconciliation is difficult Sometimes delayed
Dialogue: 4,0:27:42.40,0:27:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我认为你根本不应该过分夸大这件事
Dialogue: 3,0:27:42.40,0:27:45.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I do not think you should blow this out of proportion at all
Dialogue: 4,0:27:45.92,0:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚安
Dialogue: 3,0:27:45.92,0:27:47.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I wish you a very good evening
Dialogue: 4,0:28:02.20,0:28:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，所以他们不会刊登我的报道
Dialogue: 3,0:28:02.20,0:28:04.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah, so we have the story but they won't print it
Dialogue: 4,0:28:04.72,0:28:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是谁？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:04.72,0:28:05.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who is they?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:06.28,0:28:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉杰迪普，我们的孟买编辑不同意发表
Dialogue: 3,0:28:06.28,0:28:08.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rajdeep, our Bombay editor won't publish it
Dialogue: 4,0:28:08.36,0:28:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}迪里普，我们的总编辑想要 SBI 的确认
Dialogue: 3,0:28:08.36,0:28:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Dileep, our head editor wants a confirmation from SBI
Dialogue: 4,0:28:11.16,0:28:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说，他没有坚持要获得书面证据，但是
Dialogue: 3,0:28:11.16,0:28:13.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, he's not insisting on paper evidence but
Dialogue: 4,0:28:14.84,0:28:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和SBI的人谈过了吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:14.84,0:28:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So did you speak to anybody?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:16.16,0:28:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我直接和主席通了电话，但他否认了
Dialogue: 3,0:28:16.16,0:28:18.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes I spoke to Goiporia directly But he denied it
Dialogue: 4,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说他不会承认任何事的，对吧？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, he's not going to admit anything, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:20.08,0:28:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果说哈尔沙德犯了诈骗罪，SBI 也不是圣人
Dialogue: 3,0:28:20.08,0:28:22.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If Harshad has committed a fraud, SBI is no saint either
Dialogue: 4,0:28:22.76,0:28:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“他们也很脆弱”
Dialogue: 3,0:28:22.76,0:28:23.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'They are also vulnerable'
Dialogue: 4,0:28:24.28,0:28:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，也可能有罪，但现在怎么办？
Dialogue: 3,0:28:24.28,0:28:28.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah And possibly guilty also But what now?
Dialogue: 4,0:28:28.64,0:28:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不知道，你为什么问我?你能不能做点什么
Dialogue: 3,0:28:28.64,0:28:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't know Why are you asking me? Do something
Dialogue: 4,0:28:31.08,0:28:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我真的快没有时间了
Dialogue: 3,0:28:31.08,0:28:32.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I really don't have time
Dialogue: 4,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 喂? 喂?-喂
Dialogue: 3,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Sucheta] 'Hello? Hello?' - Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:28:36.44,0:28:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-喂-你可能也束手无策了
Dialogue: 3,0:28:36.44,0:28:39.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello -[Sucheta] 'I thought you also Anyway'
Dialogue: 4,0:28:40.80,0:28:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可能认识 SBI 的高级管理人员
Dialogue: 3,0:28:40.80,0:28:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I might know someone from SBI's senior management
Dialogue: 4,0:28:44.52,0:28:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]‘我问问他是否愿意帮助我们’
Dialogue: 3,0:28:44.52,0:28:45.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'Let me see if he can help us'
Dialogue: 4,0:28:46.08,0:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请马上和他谈谈
Dialogue: 3,0:28:46.08,0:28:47.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please, talk to him right away
Dialogue: 4,0:28:48.08,0:28:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，如果他同意，我会让他打电话给你
Dialogue: 3,0:28:48.08,0:28:49.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay If he agrees then I'll ask him to call you
Dialogue: 4,0:28:50.12,0:28:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了 谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:28:50.12,0:28:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's great Thanks
Dialogue: 4,0:29:51.16,0:29:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}马扬克，等等，你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 3,0:29:51.16,0:29:53.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mayank, wait Where are you going?
Dialogue: 4,0:29:54.16,0:29:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要去吃晚饭
Dialogue: 3,0:29:54.16,0:29:55.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm going to have dinner
Dialogue: 4,0:29:55.72,0:29:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把你的烟给我
Dialogue: 3,0:29:55.72,0:29:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Give me your pack
Dialogue: 4,0:29:58.12,0:29:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-这个行吗?-嗯
Dialogue: 3,0:29:58.12,0:29:59.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-I have this Will it do? -Hmm
Dialogue: 4,0:29:59.84,0:30:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你来吃晚饭吗?-不
Dialogue: 3,0:29:59.84,0:30:01.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You're coming for dinner? - No
Dialogue: 4,0:30:01.52,0:30:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好吧-你去
Dialogue: 3,0:30:01.52,0:30:02.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay, fine - You go
Dialogue: 4,0:30:02.56,0:30:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你会自己买一包吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:02.56,0:30:03.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and you'll buy your own pack?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:03.48,0:30:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 好的-好的谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:30:03.48,0:30:04.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Okay - Okay, thanks
Dialogue: 4,0:30:19.44,0:30:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 对不起，先生-不，请继续
Dialogue: 3,0:30:19.44,0:30:21.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Oh! Sorry, sir - No, please go on
Dialogue: 4,0:30:22.56,0:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道，在这团烟雾的背后，一定有一个非常火爆的故事
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.56,0:30:28.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know, behind this cloud of smoke, there must be a smoking hot story
Dialogue: 4,0:30:28.92,0:30:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别停，我不想打扰你的思绪
Dialogue: 3,0:30:28.92,0:30:32.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't stop I don't want to disturb your chain of thought
Dialogue: 4,0:30:33.40,0:30:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是想伸伸腿
Dialogue: 3,0:30:33.40,0:30:35.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I was just going to stretch my legs
Dialogue: 4,0:30:35.44,0:30:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，先生，没事的
Dialogue: 3,0:30:35.44,0:30:37.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, sir I'm fine, thank you
Dialogue: 4,0:30:38.08,0:30:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这年头抽烟很正常，人人都抽烟
Dialogue: 3,0:30:38.08,0:30:40.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's quite common these days, Everyone's smoking
Dialogue: 4,0:30:42.68,0:30:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顺便问一下，为什么你们普通人不抽烟？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:42.68,0:30:44.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}By the way, why doesn't your Common Man smoke?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:45.32,0:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我有哮喘-哦，这样
Dialogue: 3,0:30:45.32,0:30:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Oh! He has asthma - Oh, yes
Dialogue: 4,0:30:49.96,0:30:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我一直想问你一个问题，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:30:49.96,0:30:52.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've always wanted to ask you a question, sir
Dialogue: 4,0:30:52.96,0:30:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么你说的"普通人"总是一个男人？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:52.96,0:30:56.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why is your "Common Man" always a man?
Dialogue: 4,0:30:56.28,0:30:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么不是一个“普通女人” ？
Dialogue: 3,0:30:56.28,0:30:57.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why not a "Common Woman"?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:00.48,0:31:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，一个女人不可能是普通的
Dialogue: 3,0:31:00.48,0:31:03.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, a woman cannot be common
Dialogue: 4,0:31:04.60,0:31:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女人总是特别的
Dialogue: 3,0:31:04.60,0:31:06.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Women are always special
Dialogue: 4,0:31:06.64,0:31:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 当然-是吗？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:06.64,0:31:07.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sure - Right?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:08.92,0:31:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我想我应该……-是的，请吧
Dialogue: 3,0:31:08.92,0:31:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I think I should - Yes Please
Dialogue: 4,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喂？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:20.48,0:31:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello
Dialogue: 4,0:31:21.48,0:31:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喂，苏切塔，我要走了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:21.48,0:31:24.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello, Sucheta I'm leaving now
Dialogue: 4,0:31:24.32,0:31:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 要我送你回家吗?-不用了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:24.32,0:31:26.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Should I drop you home? - No, I'm fine
Dialogue: 4,0:31:27.36,0:31:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}贝拉里先生的故事怎么样了？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:27.36,0:31:29.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, what's the scene with Mr Bellary's story?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:29.72,0:31:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是需要一点时间
Dialogue: 3,0:31:29.72,0:31:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just need a little more time
Dialogue: 4,0:31:31.32,0:31:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“还有多少时间? ”
Dialogue: 3,0:31:31.32,0:31:32.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'How much more time?'
Dialogue: 4,0:31:33.48,0:31:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明天的报纸现在随时都可能出版
Dialogue: 3,0:31:33.48,0:31:35.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tomorrow's edition will go to print any moment now
Dialogue: 4,0:31:36.00,0:31:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可能赶不上了
Dialogue: 3,0:31:36.00,0:31:37.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I doubt if they will print the story
Dialogue: 4,0:31:37.80,0:31:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}德巴希斯，我没有心思和你争论
Dialogue: 3,0:31:37.80,0:31:39.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Debashis, I don't have the energy to argue
Dialogue: 4,0:31:39.40,0:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在等一个很重要的电话，再见
Dialogue: 3,0:31:39.40,0:31:41.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm waiting for an important phone call Bye
Dialogue: 4,0:31:43.24,0:31:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哦，不
Dialogue: 3,0:31:43.24,0:31:46.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh no Everything is a mess
Dialogue: 4,0:31:49.96,0:31:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 德巴希斯，我要告诉你多少次-达拉尔女士
Dialogue: 3,0:31:49.96,0:31:51.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Debashis, how many time do I've to tell -[Man 1] 'Ms Dalal?'
Dialogue: 4,0:31:53.04,0:31:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，对不起，你是谁？
Dialogue: 3,0:31:53.04,0:31:55.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello I'm sorry Who is this?
Dialogue: 4,0:31:55.88,0:31:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我在 SBI 工作，有人告诉我，你想和我谈谈”
Dialogue: 3,0:31:55.88,0:31:58.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man1] 'I work for SBI I was told you wanted to speak to me'
Dialogue: 4,0:31:59.08,0:32:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生，我在写一篇报道
Dialogue: 3,0:31:59.08,0:32:01.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes! Yes, sir I'm writing a story
Dialogue: 4,0:32:01.76,0:32:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我只是想-我知道细节
Dialogue: 3,0:32:01.76,0:32:03.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- and I just wanted -[Man1] 'I am aware of the details'
Dialogue: 4,0:32:04.28,0:32:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的
Dialogue: 3,0:32:04.28,0:32:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, good
Dialogue: 4,0:32:07.16,0:32:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我只需要你的确认
Dialogue: 3,0:32:07.16,0:32:09.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I just needed a confirmation from you
Dialogue: 4,0:32:10.20,0:32:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我发表了这篇文章，结果是虚惊一场
Dialogue: 3,0:32:10.20,0:32:13.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}if I publish this story, and it turns out to be a false alarm
Dialogue: 4,0:32:13.52,0:32:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我就有大麻烦了，甚至可能会丢掉工作
Dialogue: 3,0:32:13.52,0:32:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}then I'll be in very serious trouble I could even lose my job
Dialogue: 4,0:32:16.16,0:32:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“如果我的名字以任何方式突然出现，我也会丢掉工作”
Dialogue: 3,0:32:16.16,0:32:19.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man1] 'Even I'll lose my job if my name pops up in any way'
Dialogue: 4,0:32:19.52,0:32:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我不需要任何名字，我甚至不想知道细节
Dialogue: 3,0:32:19.52,0:32:22.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, I don't need any names, I don't even want the details
Dialogue: 4,0:32:22.44,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道你不能说太多
Dialogue: 3,0:32:22.44,0:32:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know you can't say much
Dialogue: 4,0:32:25.56,0:32:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只想确认我的方向是对的，先生
Dialogue: 3,0:32:25.56,0:32:28.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just need to know if I can go ahead, sir
Dialogue: 4,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续调查
Dialogue: 3,0:32:34.28,0:32:35.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go ahead
Dialogue: 4,0:32:40.20,0:32:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 3,0:32:40.20,0:32:41.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you Thank you
Dialogue: 4,0:32:46.64,0:32:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太好了
Dialogue: 3,0:32:46.64,0:32:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes
Dialogue: 4,0:33:28.52,0:33:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，我读了你的文章
Dialogue: 3,0:33:28.52,0:33:30.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, I read your piece
Dialogue: 4,0:33:31.80,0:33:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}诈骗这个词出现了很多次
Dialogue: 3,0:33:31.80,0:33:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You've used this word "scam" so many times
Dialogue: 4,0:33:34.52,0:33:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说我们只用金融丑闻之类的词
